overview: October 18th, 2008 :: CHIKARA collides with Big Japan Wrestling in a "Best of 5" Series, plus a tag team match pitting Chikara's The Osirian Portal against BJW's Atsushi Ohashi and Shinya Ishikawa! The finals of La Loteria Letal are decided when Lince Dorado and Jimmy Olsen wrestle The UnStable! Matches featured:  1. Osirian Portal vs Atsushi Ohashi & Shinya Ishikawa  2. Yuji Okabayashi vs Ultimo Breakfast  3. Jaki Numazawa vs UltraMantis Black  4. Katsumasa Inoue vs Hallowicked  5. Crossbones, Ryan Eagles & Madison Eagles vs Jessie McKay & The Colony  6.
